We can rewrite $2007^3$ as the cube of a binomial: \begin{align*}
2007^3 &= (2\cdot 10^3 + 7)^3\\
&= \binom{3}{0} (2\cdot 10^3)^3 + \cdots + \binom{3}{3} 7^3
\end{align*}

